data.description: Mixed use commercial and residential building located in the heart of Downtown Baltimore. Just blocks away from downtown and the Inner Harbor this well kept building features first floor commercial space with three apartments over top. Two out of the three apartments are currently rented. apartment is currently rented. The three apartment are made up of 1 - One Bedroom apartment and 2- Two bedroom apartments. Each apartment comes with hardwood floors, central air, stove, refrigerator, disposal, washer and dryer, recess lights and much more. The one bedroom units is currently rented for $1,000, The two bedroom is currently rented for $1,200 and top floor unit which is listed for $1,275. The commercial space is renting for $1,275 and is listed by a smoke shop. Everyone is current and on time with there rent at this point. We can provide you with current rent rolls. The rental license and lead certificates are uploaded. The two bedroom apartments come with two bathrooms.
